<title>skyb ạlrwḥ</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr- ạ̉skb skyb ạlrwḥ .. ạ̉mly̱ ạlnfws bạlrwḥ
 kẖlṣ ạ̹sẖfy ạlmjrwḥ .. ạ̉skb skyb
 1- ạ̉skb skyb ạlrwḥ .. wtʿạl fy wsṭynạ
 qds wạlms bạlrwḥ .. bmwạhb fyḍ fynạ
 mn lmjd lmjd tạkẖdnạ .. bsḥạb ạlmjd tqwdnạ
 lyk wḥdk kl sjwdnạ .. yạ mlk ạlmlwk
 2- ạ̉skb skyb ạlrwḥ .. wtʿạl lạ̉rạḍynạ
 fy bldnạ ạlḥq nsẖwf .. fy jylnạ yạ fạdynạ
 nkẖrj brh ạlạ̉swạr .. nkẖṭf mn qlb ạlnạr
 ạ̉sẖrạr ybqwạ ạ̉brạr .. wạlmjd tạny yʿwd
 3- ạ̉skb skyb ạlrwḥ .. yạ ṣạnʿ ạlmʿjzạt
 wfy kl mkạn hạnrwḥ .. bạsmk nṣnʿ ậyạt
 ạ̉ḥzạnnạ ḥmlthạ .. ạ̉mrạḍnạ sẖfythạ
 wạllʿnẗ ksrthạ .. wạlsẖkwy̱ ṭrḥthạ</lyrics>
